Project 2 Backend


Project Overview
This project is a backend server for managing recipes and favorite recipes. It provides a RESTful API for creating, reading, updating, and deleting recipes. Additionally, users can mark recipes as favorites and retrieve random meals from an external API.

Features
- Create, read, update, and delete recipes.
- Mark recipes as favorites.
- Fetch a random meal from an external API.
- List meals by first letter.
- List meal categories.

